window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The beautiful monster girls of the Archipelagos were in need. </p> <p>They needed a man to help build their homes. </p> <p>They needed a man to teach them to survive. </p> <p>They needed a man to defend them from the evil slaver-pirates. </p> <p>And most of all, they needed a man to impregnate them and rebuild their population. </p> <p>Fortunately for them, a man named Ben came from our world to give them everything they needed. </p>"; 
